briefTitle: Autologous Muscle Derived Cells for Female Urinary Sphincter Repair
officialTitle: A Double-blind, Randomized, Controlled Trial Comparing the Safety and Efficacy of AMDC-USR With Placebo in Female Subjects With Stress Urinary Incontinence
summary: This randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, multicenter, confirmatory study will evaluate the efficacy and safety of Cook MyoSite Incorporated Autologous Muscle-Derived Cells (generic name Iltamiocel) compared to a placebo (vehicle) control dose in the treatment of stress urinary incontinence (SUI) in adult female patients.
